Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.transaction.log.files.checkpoint

Interface CheckpointFile

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Lifecycle, RotatableFile
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CheckpointLogFile, CompositeCheckpointLogFile
    public interface CheckpointFile
extends Lifecycle, RotatableFile
    Access to underlying store checkpoints, that can be stored in multiple log files, separate log files etc.
